code: @Override public SearchRequestBuilder prepareSearch(String... indices) {     SearchRequestBuilder searchRequestBuilder = in.prepareSearch(indices).setSearchType(defaultSearchType).setPreference(defaultPreference).setBatchedReduceSize(batchedReduceSize).     if (maxConcurrentShardRequests != -1) {         searchRequestBuilder.setMaxConcurrentShardRequests(maxConcurrentShardRequests).     }     if (preFilterShardSize != -1) {         searchRequestBuilder.setPreFilterShardSize(preFilterShardSize).     }     if (doTimeout) {         searchRequestBuilder.setTimeout(new TimeValue(1, TimeUnit.DAYS)).     }     return searchRequestBuilder. }
